com.ibm.mq.explorer.ms0s.mqsceditor.gui

Class MQSCCompletionProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.mq.explorer.ms0s.mqsceditor.gui.MQSCCompletionProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.jface.text.contentassist.IContentAssistProcessor

    public class MQSCCompletionProcessor
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.eclipse.jface.text.contentassist.IContentAssistProcessor

    This reacts to requests for code completion and produces the relevant suggestions based on where in the MQSC command the request came from. It uses MQSC Command Event objects attaced to each parser token to determine what values to retrieve from the MQSC Language configuration.
